## Environment credentials
Use GTM Lookup Table variable (Input: Page Hostname) to switch credentials between UAT and production. Never hardcode credentials.

## CleverTap SDK Loader HTML
```html
<script type="text/javascript">
  var clevertap = {event:[],profile:[],account:[],onUserLogin:[],notifications:[],privacy:[]};
  clevertap.account.push({"id":"{{CT - Account ID}}"});
  clevertap.region = "in1";
  clevertap.privacy.push({optOut:false});
  clevertap.privacy.push({useIP:false});
  (function(){var w=document.createElement('script');w.type='text/javascript';w.async=true;
  w.src='https://d2r1yp2w7bby2u.cloudfront.net/js/clevertap.min.js';
  var s=document.getElementsByTagName('script')[0];s.parentNode.insertBefore(w,s);})();
</script>
```

## Testing checklist
1. `window.google_tag_manager` → object with container ID
2. SDK Loader tags in Tags Fired on page load
3. `typeof clevertap` → "object"
4. Event row in GTM Preview with tag green
5. No DLVs showing undefined
6. Event in platform debugger within 10s

